result.name: May Do Cafe

reviews.text: Food is expensive if compared to other restaurants but the important thing is that the service is bad ,I think the cashier is the boss ,his shouted to his staff, pity I saw the auntie scolded by him. The way that he treats the staff is rude, one star for the boss,actually your attitude are worth lower than that ,i had a very bad experience there.

Cantonese style restaurant
People are good compared to other busy area eg. Mongkok, Tst
Neighborhood restaurant. Portion is big, pretty good choice of meals. This restaurant has the space constraints like their counterpart.  The waitressing is good, nice and patience.  Good play to eat.

It is a typical local Chinese family style cafe serving the most traditional Cantonese style food with boiled soup. Lots of old people would prefer dining here instead of cooking at home. The reason I dine in occasionally mainly for the old Hong Kong dining culture. I can enjoy a cup of “rich tea and milk”, overheard the conversation of staff, background music from radio instead of piping music, more human connection and a place less commerical. The taste of food is plain. A deep fried fish slices with corn and a cup of milk and tea charged $65. In fact, there are better options in KT.

Not many this type of cafe survives in Kwun Tong. I wish they can sustain business the next time I visit again.
ok😊

result.adr_address: 香港觀塘協和街93號G/F
result.name: 美都茶餐廳

reviews.text: 價錢比其他餐廳貴15%，食材普通料。
陪外母一早抽血，因為要禁食，美都就在對面馬路，抽完馬上過去食早餐，算係觀塘老字號，阿姐服務好好，但食物就冇特別，其實可以話水準之下。
食物質素下降， 份量偏少， 衛生問題差， 有圖有真相， 凍檸檬茶 杯底 千年污漬。
普及大眾化的餐廳。價錢並不便宜。
觀塘一間懷舊嘅茶餐廳，由細食到老…一個字正
